"{\"uid\": \"jamaicaobserver.com-2024-07-23-france-intercepting-6-drones-daily-near-olympic-sites-pm\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"V\\u00c9LIZY-VILLACOUBLAY,\\u00a0France\\u00a0(AFP)- French security forces guarding sites set to be used in the Paris Olympics are intercepting an average of six drones per day, Prime Minister Gabriel Attal said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21, \"end\": 27, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.997274190735678, \"rank\": 0.0027259829861926124, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gabriel Attal\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gabriel_Attal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The miniature flyers are sometimes operated by \\\"individuals, maybe tourists wanting to take pictures\\\", Attal said.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 311, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's why it's important to remind people of the rules.\", \"from\": 313, \"to\": 370, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a ban on flying drones,\\\" he added during a visit to the event's drone defence hub at Velizy-Villacoublay air base outside Paris.\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 508, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999247393, \"rank\": 7.520899155955478e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Systems are in place to allow us to very quickly intercept (drones) and arrest their operators,\\\" Attal said.\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We can not allow anything to slip past us.\\\"\", \"from\": 620, \"to\": 664, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He highlighted several incidents around the Olympic village on Sunday.\", \"from\": 666, \"to\": 736, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"According to a member of Attal's team, the communications chief of the Brazilian delegation was apprehended over operating a drone.\", \"from\": 737, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Any unauthorised drone will be jammed,\\\" said Stephane Groen, France's general in charge of air defence, as Attal visited a control room where an aerial vehicle had been spotted over the Stade de France stadium.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.997274190735678, \"rank\": 0.0027259829861926124, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The defenders' job is particularly tricky as they must avoid the remote vehicles falling while a sporting event is underway.\", \"from\": 1083, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nevertheless, \\\"if in doubt, we always jam\\\" a drone, Defence Minister Sebastien Lecornu said.\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1261, \"end\": 1277, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Defence_minister\", \"score\": 0.9999992331325515, \"rank\": 7.66868044923083e-07, \"text\": \"Defence Minister\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Defence_minister\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Defence_minister\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As well as drone defences, other forms of anti-aircraft defence are in place around Olympic sites.\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Around 18,000 French troops have been deployed to secure the Olympics, 11,000 of them in the Ile-de-France region around Paris.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1530, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1417, \"end\": 1423, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9965765539017346, \"rank\": 0.0016841284208323364, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1524, \"end\": 1529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999247393, \"rank\": 7.520899155955478e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a French first, airspace in a 150-kilometre (93 miles) radius around Paris will be completely closed on Friday evening during the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1682, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1604, \"end\": 1609, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999247393, \"rank\": 7.520899155955478e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tags:  HOUSE RULES\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": []}]}"